body:
### Welcome to the individual project for CSS350 made by Konstantin Stekhov.
This website contains a dictionary full of the terms and definitions from our textbook. Also, it has summaries of the important chapters from our textbooks. Finally, it is just a great source of information available to anyone who wants to learn the basic management principals.
